{"tid":2429603,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"今日返工，條撚樣屌鳩我","createTime":"2021-03-02T12:20:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-03T01:54:48.000Z","uid":355915,"like":23,"dislike":92,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"b880963ac1c629e1698c75269ace527bc6639380","tid":2429603,"uid":355915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T12:20:12.000Z","msg":"條柒頭拖條女黎做檢測，咁我幫佢條女填資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要睇佢手機預約message，條女手機又暗，我咪行近d睇。點知條撚樣即刻話：「你哄咁撚埋做乜撚野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你識唔撚識㗎」屌你老母你唔撚識字，我幫你條女填仲要俾你屌？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我啤一啤佢，點知佢即刻掉頭死撚左去對面馬路<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />剩低條女係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我果陣無屌撚柒翻佢，因為太多人排緊隊，要幫好多人填資料。轉過頭唔見左條撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔係我屌撚到你老母個閪都爛<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講緊你呀柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />做咩死撚左去對面馬路啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82c669b9762098885c70e868c13dad3542c8d9d4","tid":2429603,"uid":355915,"like":11,"dislike":7,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T12:21:56.000Z","msg":"遇到閪客必須毫不留情地屌佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd58ecb8cb61852a97702672371bae9336de4bce","tid":2429603,"uid":24432,"like":104,"dislike":1,"score":103,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T12:26:54.000Z","msg":"個陣無屌柒返佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n結果咪上連登做鍵盤戰士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d4e67b86d7bb0ede03b783bc7298d0ffa77f184","tid":2429603,"uid":355915,"like":1,"dislike":21,"score":-20,"quote":{"pid":"bd58ecb8cb61852a97702672371bae9336de4bce","tid":2429603,"uid":24432,"like":104,"dislike":1,"score":103,